4. Rewards & Character Progression
This system uses milestone-based Advancement Points (AP) rather than XP: players earn AP for completing a story milestone (typically 1 AP per completed adventure).
Dragon Kills (standing bonus rule — dragons are always worth more):
Regular dragon: 2 AP to the character who lands the killing blow; 1 AP to every other participant.
Elder dragon: 4 AP for the killing blow; 2 AP for participation.

